Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Muenzanise huwandu hwehupenyu hwehupenyu, hunosanganisira magetsi emagetsi, maitiro ekugadzirisa, zviratidzo zvekutsinhanisa, masero ekubatanidza masero, mashizha ezvokudya, nezvimwewo zvine chokuita nezvisikwa zvakasiyana-siyana zvinobva kubhakitiriya kuenda kune mavairasi kuenda kunezizi kuti zvive kuvanhu. Tsanangura mafungiro asina chikonzero chekupinda kana kugadzirisa zvakaoma mashematical equations.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Shandisa nguva chaiyo, inobatanidza kuenzanisira kuenzanisa maitiro ehupenyu hwehupenyu pasi pemhando dzakasiyana-siyana dzepascellular uyewo mutano (i.e., chirwere). Mhanya mazana ezvikuenzanisa zviongorori munyaya yemaminitsi uye ita maitiro ekutsvaga-kubudisa maonero ekuona mapeji emitemo pasi pemamiriro akasiyana
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Ongorora mafungiro uye mhinduro dzezvigadzirwa zvehupenyu pasi pemamiriro akasiyana. Runza-system-kupoteredza kuongororwa kutsvaga kufanotaura uye kutarisa migumisiro yevanhu pachavo uye kusanganiswa kwezvikamu pane system. Gadzirira uye tsvakurudza zvinodhaka zvezvezvekuita zvinodhaka uye combinatorial therapy mikana.

Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.YouMayC: Iwe unogona kuvhara {photo} icon panguva ipi zvayo kuti udzidze nezvezvinhu zvakawanda zveSunction Collective.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Dzvanya pamufananidzo kuti uende pakati pe {photo1} (View Mode) uye {photo2} (Edit Mode). <ol> <li> Kamwe kaviri kanda pane nzvimbo isina chinhu kuti uwedzere chinhu chitsva. </ li> <li> Dhinda Chengetedza Label kuti udzoke zvakare chikamu. </ li> <li> Shift + Kurudyi kuronga kuti uchinje mukati kana kunze kwemashoko. </ li> <li> Shandura pakati pekubatana kwakanaka kana kusakanganiswa neShift + -kudhonza-kuruboshwe kumutsara wokubatanidza. </ li> </ ol>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.NewMod: Zvitsva zvinyorwa zvitsva zvinogonawo kuwedzerwa nekutsvaira pano pa {photo}. Bhinda kaviri kateti kuti uite zita remutauro.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Kuwedzera an activator kana inhibitor, dhonza uye udzike zvikamu kubva pakurongwa kweInternal Components kana External Components kune Drop Component dialog box. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Dzvanya pa {photo} icon kuti uchengetedze kuchinja kwako.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Shandisa slide shoma kuti uise mamiriro ekunze (kureva maitiro ekuenzanisa). Nharaunda dzinogonawo kuva dzakasiyana panguva yekufananidza kufungidzira machinjeko mumasimba emamiriro ezvinhu munguva chaiyo. Izvi zvakafananidza nekusiyana kwemamiriro ehupenyu hwehupenyu nekucherechedza mhinduro dzayo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Sarudza bhokisi riri pasi apa kuonekwa {photo} icon yezvikamu zvaunoda kufungidzira paGirafu yekufananidza. Kuenderera mberi pamusoro peiyo tsamba ichajekesa maitiro ayo, zvichikubvumira kuti uwane zvakananga chikamu mukati mefaira rakawanda!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Dzvanya {photo1} icon kuti utange kuenzanisa. Iwe unogonawo kuvhara {photo2} kuti usimbise kuenzanisa chero nguva ipi zvayo kana kudzorera kuenzanisa nekudhonza pa {photo3} icon.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Dzvanya pa {photo} icon kuti uite chiitiko chitsva. Ongororo dzinodanwa zvakare zvakananga kuburikidza nekodhinda.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Shandisa slide shoma kuti ugadzire mamiriro ekunze (kureva maitiro ekuenzanisa) nokuda kwekuedza. Izvi zvakafananidza nekuisa zviratidzo zvekunze kwehupenyu hwehupenyu hwehupenyu huri mukati mehupenyu hwahwo, hunoita kuti zviratidzo zvayo zviitike. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Dzvanya pa {photo} iicon kuti utange kuenzanisa.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Dose-mhinduro magrafu inogona kugadzirwa chero ipi zvayo mumutambo nekusarudza chikamu chakakodzera che X uye Y-axis. Nenzira yakawanda, chimwe chinhu chiri kunze chinomiririrwa pane X-axis (iyo pendent variable) asi zvikamu zvemukati zvinomiririrwa pa-Y-axis (mhando dzakasiyana). Multiple dose-response curves inogona kugadzirwa kubva pane imwe yero. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> Unogona kutsvaga maenzaniso nemusoro, tsanangudzo, tema kana proteinini zita. Mhinduro imwe chete ichatsvaga Published Pubels, My Models, uye Yakagovana neni Me catalogs panguva imwechete. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> Unogona kushandura maonero ako pakati pekuona mazita uye grid kuona. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> Mune menyu unogona kuchinja yako user profile, shandura password yako, uye logout. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Mamiriro (kana SubConditions) anoshandiswa kuenzanisa kubatana kana kusawirirana kune mumwe kana vamwe vanobatana navo. Dhaira kuwedzera icon kuti uzarure Zvirongwa zvepanamato, dhonza uye udzike zvikamu zvakakodzera pane (kuderedza chikamu) bhokisi rekukurukurirana uye tsanangura kana Chiitiko chinofanira kunge Chine Active kana Chisingabviri. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Mienzaniso inotsanangurwa uye inotsanangurwa uchishandisa Knowledge Base. Dzvanya pa {photo1} kuwedzera zviri mukati uye {photo2} kuwedzera zvinyorwa. Ingopinda mubhuku rinonzi PubMed Identifier (PMID) kuti usvike mafaira uye unganise zvinyorwa. Tsanangudzo dzinogona kuiswa maererano nekudhindwa uye kudarika. Tsvaga-chengetedza-chengetedza pane zviri kutaurwa uye sarudza tag yaunoda kuwedzera.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Kubatana chinhu chikuru chekuwana zvitsva kuburikidza nekugadzirisa nzira - uye iri pamwoyo we Cell Collective! Kushanda pa {photo} kunokuendesa kugovera peji, zvichikugonesa kuwedzera vashandi, kuumba zvibatanidza zvinobatanidzwa uye kuparidzira kuongorora.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Sarudza icho chaunoda kuchinja. Kushandura bhokisi kamwechete kurasikirwa-kwe-basa mutation (inoratidzwa nebhokisi rekutsvaga), uye kubhota bhokisi kaviri inoshandiswa-in-function mutation (inoratidzirwa nechokufukidzira chemavara). Kushandura kachitatu kunobvisa kuchinja. Kuchinja-chinja kunogona kuendeswa mberi kana panguva yekufananidza kufungidzira kuchinja kwemasimba munguva chaiyo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Dzvanya {photo} kuti uite nyika yekutanga. Kana imwe yenyika yekutanga yakasikwa, chiratidzo chinoratidzwa mukati mePakini Inhengo dzePakiti. Kubva munharaunda iyi, sarudza zvinhu zvaunoda kushanda pakutanga kwekufananidza (t = 0).

Dzvanya {photo} kuti unyore kutenderera kwekuenzanisa. Icho chiratidzo chichashanduka chigadzirwa kamwe chete apo zvinyorwa zviri kuenderera mberi. Kuchinja mumamiriro ezvinhu ekuedza kana kuchinja, uye nguva yavo yekutsvaga-nguva inoitika, yakanyorwa uye yakachengetedzwa mukati mekuyerera kwekufananidzirwa, zvichiita kuti kuvezve kushandiswa kwezviongororwa zvepassetse.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Zviongoridzo zvakawanda zvinogona kusarudzwa uchishandisa mabhokisi ekuongorora. Kana ukasarudzwa, unogona kubvisa, kukopa, kana kudzorerazve zvidzidzo panguva imwe chete. Izvi zvinonyanya kukosha pakugadzirisa kuongororwa mushure mokuita shanduko kune muenzaniso wekugadzirisa nzira. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Dzvanya {photo} pedyo nekutarisa Mvura. Kuongorora kushandiswa kwekuenzanisa hakukwanisi kunyorwa, saka, mamiriro ezvinhu kunze (izvo zvinopindira) kana kuchinja-chinja, uye mararamiro avo (i.e. nguva-nzvimbo zviitiko) inofanirwa kunge yakanyorwa kare. Verenga tutorial Simulation Runs for more details.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Kana uine girafu rinowanikwa pano unogona kukopa Izvo Basa Relationship Girafu sefini yePNG nekukanya pano. </ span>
